attributes.name: OriginalStatement
attributes.text: Describe a system for purifying dirty water. - Heat dirty water and condense steam are performed by a Counter Flow Heat Exchanger - Boil dirty water is performed by a Boiler. Drain residue is performed by a Drain. The water has properties: vol = 1 liter, density 1 gm/cm3, temp 20 deg C, specific heat 1cal/gm deg C, heat of vaporization 540 cal/gm.
